2. fatih/color (API inspiration)
   Source:  https://github.com/fatih/color
   License: MIT
   Files:   internal/termcolor/color.go

   The termcolor package is a from-scratch implementation using ANSI escape
   codes, inspired by the API conventions of fatih/color. No code was copied.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

3. go-multihash (wire format knowledge)
   Source:  https://github.com/multiformats/go-multihash
   License: MIT
   Files:   internal/invite/code.go (strictMultihashLen function)

   The multihash validation uses the publicly documented multihash wire format
   (varint-code, varint-length, digest) with Go's stdlib encoding/binary. No
   code was copied from the go-multihash library.
